channel.title: The Hit List
channel.desc: It's time for the stars to shine in another celebrity special. The famous faces joining Rochelle and Marvin Humes in this episode of the addictive music quiz are comedians Ivo Graham and Emmanuel Sonubi, musician Toyah Willcox and ex-footballer Pat Nevin, and EastEnders stars Natalie Cassidy and Jamie Borthwick. Who will guess the song titles first and get the chance to win ?10,000 for their chosen charity?
